Subject: OKT-MISC-0000004-TE

1. It should be possible to assign a routine in the pattern in order
   to make advanced filtering.

2. It is suggested to allow force CSAP to generate invalid (specific)
  field values.

3. Each CSAP should be implemented as defined structure which may
  use external libraries for lower layers.

4. It should be possible to use traffic generation library on Test
  Engine side in order view raw packet from test.


Subject: OKT-WBS-0000029-TE

1. Creation of notification mechanism should be motivated.

2. It should be possible to use "failures" option in Report Generator
  configuration.
